value.title: TechCrunch Disrupt 2026: Plus-one passes are almost gone and only 3 days remain
value.content: The TechCrunch Disrupt 2026 plus-one passes at 50% off are almost sold out, and this deal ends in 3 days. Register here before this deal ends on Friday, January 30 at 11:59 p.m. PT.

value.title: The conference where founders scale: TechCrunch Founder Summit 2026 tickets are now live at the lowest prices
value.content: TechCrunch Founder Summit 2026 unites 1,100 founders and investors in Boston on June 23 for a day focused on real-world scaling insights and networking that pushes the needle. Save up to $300 on your ticket.

value.title: Vinod Khosla publicly disavows Keith Rabois’ comments on ICE shooting
value.content: Unwavering Trump loyalist and VC Keith Rabois caused his colleague  and his firm's founder to distance themselves from his comments on ICE.

value.title: Obvious Ventures lands fund five with a 360-degree view of planetary, human, economic health
value.content: The 12-year-old firm raised $360,360,360 for its fifth fund. And there's a reason for that number.

value.title: VC firm 2150 raises €210M fund to solve cities’ climate challenges
value.content: Europe-based venture fund 2150 raised the money to invest in climate tech startups that help solve cities' carbon footprint.

value.title: Only 5 days left: Over half of the first 500 TechCrunch Disrupt 2026 plus-one passes at 50% off are already gone
value.content: Register now to save up to $680 on your TechCrunch Disrupt 2026 pass and get a +1 ticket at 50% off. Offer ends this Friday, January 30.

value.title: What is Bending Spoons? The little-known firm behind Vimeo’s sweeping layoffs
value.content: Bending Spoons remains largely unknown, even as its portfolio of products has served more than a billion people.

value.content: Register now to save up to $680 on your TechCrunch Disrupt 2026 pass and get a second ticket at 50% off. This offer ends next week on January 30, or once the first 500 tickets are claimed — whichever comes first.

value.title: Former Sequoia partner’s new startup uses AI to negotiate your calendar for you
value.content: Blockit, an AI agent that communicates directly with other calendars, has raised $5 million in seed funding led by Sequoia.

value.title: Voice AI engine and OpenAI partner LiveKit hits $1B valuation
value.content: The five-year-old-startup powers OpenAI’s ChatGPT voice mode and raised a $100 million round led by Index Ventures.

value.title: Inference startup Inferact lands $150M to commercialize vLLM
value.content: The seed round values the newly formed startup at $800 million.

value.title: Former CEO of celeb fav gym Dogpound launches $5M fund to back wellness companies
value.content: Jenny Liu is a solo first-time GP looking to back underrepresented wellness founders.
